# PulseBoard

A full-stack real-time polling application built with the MERN stack. Users can create polls, share them via a unique link, collect responses, and view live analytics — all without requiring respondents to log in.

---

## Features

- JWT-based authentication (register, login, protected routes)
- Create polls with multiple questions, custom options, and expiry dates
- Mandatory question enforcement on submission
- Anonymous and authenticated response modes
- Unique share token per poll for public access
- Real-time analytics updates via Socket.io
- Bar chart visualizations using Recharts
- Publish/unpublish poll control
- Auto-expiry based on a configurable date

---

## Tech Stack

**Frontend**
- React (Vite)
- Tailwind CSS
- React Router
- Axios
- Recharts
- Socket.io Client
- React Hot Toast

**Backend**
- Node.js
- Express
- MongoDB with Mongoose
- Socket.io
- JWT (jsonwebtoken)
- bcryptjs

---

